    <p><anchor n="T.50.2059.0416b20"/><lb ed="T" n="0416b20"/><persName key="A003524">釋慧芬</persName>，姓李，<placeName key="PL000000026339">豫州</placeName>人。幼有殊操，<date key="j18737331874097" from-iso="0418-01-02" to-iso="0419-01-01">十二</date>出家，<lb ed="T" n="0416b21"/>住<placeName key="PL000000025651">穀熟縣常山寺</placeName>。學業優深，苦行精峻。每赴<lb ed="T" n="0416b22"/>齋會，常為大眾說法。<placeName key="PL000000043862">梁</placeName><placeName key="PL000000027944">楚</placeName>之間，悉奉其化。<lb ed="T" n="0416b23"/>及<persName key="A002596">魏虜</persName>毀滅佛法，乃南歸<ptr target="fn13"/><placeName key="PL000000008976">京師</placeName>。至<placeName key="PL000000016248">烏江</placeName>，<lb ed="T" n="0416b24"/>追騎將及而渚次無航，<persName key="A003524">芬</persName>一心念佛，俄見<lb ed="T" n="0416b25"/>流船忽至，乘之獲免。至<placeName key="PL000000008976">都</placeName>，止<placeName key="PL000000008691">白馬寺</placeName>。時御<lb ed="T" n="0416b26"/>史中丞<persName key="A003525">袁愍孫</persName>常謂道人偏執，未足與議，乃<lb ed="T" n="0416b27"/>命左右，令候覓沙門，試<ptr target="fn14"/>欲<ptr target="fn15"/>語之。會得<persName key="A003524">芬</persName><lb ed="T" n="0416b28"/>至，<persName key="A003525">袁</persName>先問三乘四諦之理，却辯老莊儒墨<lb ed="T" n="0416b29"/>之要。<persName key="A003524">芬</persName>既素善經書，又音吐流便。自旦<lb ed="T" n="0416c01"/>之夕，袁不能窮。於是敬以為師，令子弟悉<lb ed="T" n="0416c02"/>從受戒。</p><p><persName key="A003524">芬</persName>又善神呪，所治必驗。後病篤，服<lb ed="T" n="0416c03"/><ptr target="fn16"/>丸，人<ptr target="fn17"/>勸之以酒。<persName key="A003524">芬</persName>曰：「積時持戒，寧以<lb ed="T" n="0416c04"/>將<ptr target="fn18"/>死虧節。」乃語弟子云：「<persName key="A003524">吾</persName>其去矣。」以<date key="j18982361898589" from-iso="0485-02-02" to-iso="0486-01-21">齊<lb ed="T" n="0416c05"/>永明三年</date>卒于興福寺，年七十九。臨終有<lb ed="T" n="0416c06"/>訓誡遺文云云。</p>
